Soul Burn
deal damage over time also reducing their attack damage as well. Enemys will take damage if they cast any spells or items by x1.2 x1.3
x1.4 x1.5 of their mana cost plus Soul Burn total damage. Soul Burn will Ignore Status Resistence but can be Purge.

